modName: Female Enemy Monster Aesthetics Leveled Encounters - More Sexy Creatures
summary:
F.E.M.A.L.E. Female Enemy Monster Aesthetics Leveled Encounters

Adds a variety new and more creatures Lore Leveled List encounters, new beatiful girl (sexy or scared?) female enemy in Skyrim wolrd. Not only beatiful look, but also improved gamplay difficult. Its like Skyrim Immersive Creatures or MonterMod but only FEMALE.

[center][/center][b][color=#ff00ff]Description[/color][/b]:
Simply add a Female Enemy Monster in the world! I consider it Lore... but probably someone might disagree!

Female Enemy Monster Aesthetics Leveled Encounters aka F.E.M.A.L.E. adds a new variety monster enemy on Skyrim World with new concept creatures, all monster girls are in variants LeveledList, based on lore game, for example Dwarven Doll are in Dwarven LevelList, Undead Female are in Draugr LevelList, Lady of Bones are in Skeleton LevelList, etc... its like Skyrim Immersive Creatures or MonsterMod, but only with FEMALE! Enjoy!

I have added in leveled list for random encounter based on your level also gameplay are too hard, hope I have not made ​​any mistakes, but i think work correctly.. i have also edited and modified some meshes and more.

New spell with integration of Tome! You can find the Book Spell for conjure some new creatures.

Recommended use Wrye Bash
and for load order place last or after any creatures mod (like Skyrim Immersive Creature)

I have tested with 200++ mod and work good for me.

Main Files - FEMALE.esp
Optional - FEMALE-DLCaddon.esp - (for Dawnguard and Dragonborn)
Optional NoSpider - FEMALE.esp - (remove Daedra Spider and Arachne Queen)

[color=#ff00ff][b]Know issues and bug[/b][/color]:
Hands Female Undead no have textures for now
Fighting style is not appropriate to the creature (spriggan, dwarven etc.)
Some Draugr Male Boss can have Female Undead aesthetics (like Gauldur for example)
[s]Flame Atronach have not effect fire and on dead, i work to create appropriate effect like Flame Atronach (with small script)[/s]

If you have issue whit Draconian Hybrid (base race argonian) you can download this:
[url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/4686]CBBE-CHSBHC-UNP-ADEC-Human Argonian Khajiit Texture [/url]or [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/11400]UNP Khajiit and Argonian Hotfix[/url] (i use this)

If you have installed one of these armors, or a mod that uses them, might be reported as playable characters and then you can loot, this changing the look of the creature, i suggest you do not loot (only armor) to avoid problems, especially for Dwarven Doll and Gynoid, or try change load order, but this make armor non-playable, you decide what to do.

[b][color=#ff00ff]Installation[/color][/b]:
use NMM or drop Data folder to Skyrim

[b][color=#ff00ff]Upgrade[/color][/b]:
For vrs 2.0 and above - install/upgrade new version, wait in location without enemy (your home for example) for cell reset, or if you have other mod with MCM menù with cell reset option use it (like Deadly Dragon for example..)!
For vrs 1.0 - uninstall version 1.0 and Install other NEW version or not work! I have renamed .esp (only if you have vrs 1.0)

[b][color=#ff00ff]UnInstallation[/color][/b]:
use NMM or remove files (look archives)
